      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under documented version control with traceable build records and regression test suite passing.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is under institutional version control. A regression test suite of 47 benchmark cases was executed and all passed prior to the study. Software release notes and build hashes are archived in the project repository, satisfying Gradation 2 requirements for MRL 2."
    },
    {
