      "rationale": "The k-omega SST turbulence model and Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model are established in peer-reviewed literature for centrifugal pump hemolysis prediction. Formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 and is not assessed."
    },
    {
