      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles for CFD were derived from ultrasonic flow meter measurements at the pump inlet plane. Outlet pressure boundary conditions matched the experimental backpressure within 2 mmHg. Equivalency of all primary input parameters was confirmed by direct comparison of CFD setup files against experimental data acquisition records."
