    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within 12.4% of experimental measurements across the full COU operating envelope, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Six factors were not assessed per the approved MRL 2 assessment plan. The grid convergence study results, discussed in the discretization error factor rationale, confirm mesh-independent predictions with GCI of 1.3%. The credibility assessment team accepts the model for the stated COU.",
